* Arnulf Rainer Museum, Baden
* Arnulf Rainer at the Museum of Modern Art. MoMa - The Collection, New York
* Arnulf Rainer at Galerie Lelong, Paris
* Arnulf Rainer at the Galerie m Bochum, Bochum</text><links>
