* &quot;Lower Yourself&quot; (1997) – Citadel
* &quot;We Got This!&quot; (2002) – Laughing Outlaw
* &quot;Gloria&quot; (May 2009) – Impedance
* &quot;Incantations&quot; (2014) – Impedance

===Extended plays===

* &quot;Pedestal&quot; (October 1994) – Lance Rock
* &quot;Woe Betide&quot; (November 1995) – Lance Rock

===Live albums===

