*&quot;Live&quot; (2014) – Pitshark

===Compilations===

* &quot;Detritus&quot; (EP, 1987) – What Goes On
* &quot;Divine Rites&quot; (1988) – Citadel
* &quot;Born Out of Time&quot; (1995) – Lance Rock
* &quot;These Rags&quot; (2002) – Citadel

