<doc id="700963" wikidata="Q3489488" url="?curid=700963" title="Nipesotsu-Maruyama Volcanic Group">
<text>Nipesotsu-Maruyama is a volcanic group situated in Hokkaidō, Japan.

It is composed of several stratovolcanoes and lava domes, including:

* Mount Nipesotsu
* Mount Maru (Kamishihoro-Shintoku)
* Mount Tengu
* Mount Kotengu
* Mount Gunkan
* 1332 Meter Peak
* Mount Upepesanke

